<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Thank you for using our services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #8DBBFA;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Thank You for Your Appointment Booking!</h2>
        <p>Dear Customer,</p>
        <p>Thank you for scheduling an appointment with us. Here are the details:</p>
        <p><strong>Doctor's name:</strong> {{doctor}}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{startTime}} - {{endTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{type}}</p>
        <p>Please wait for a confirmation email with further details.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>SoulCare Team</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
